      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "范蠡上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00002",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "引子",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "吴越构兵，愿吾主，定霸称雄。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00003",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "列国纷纷起战争，兵戈未息尽强邻。若能洗净君王耻，方算朝中干蛊臣。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00004",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "下官，姓范名蠡，字表少伯，楚宛人氏。生性倜傥，玩世佯狂。幼习阴符妙术，长学战策权谋。久离乡井，周历列国。幸遇越王勾践，拔之于众人之中，厕之以大夫之上，志同道合，言听计从。可恨吴王夫差，欺凌我国，将吾君臣，囚于石室，三载有余。幸我国大夫文种，进以珠宝，赎我君臣还朝。至今未雪此耻。那夫差本是酒色之徒，意欲寻访美女，献于吴邦，蛊惑吴王，改坏朝政，叫他自取灭亡，以报当年会稽之仇。闻听人言，此地苎萝村内有两个美人，一个叫做东施，一个叫做西施，美貌无比。吾不免微服出游，寻访一回，有何不可？出得门来，看这峰山竞秀，万壑争流。正是：",
      "text_length": 261
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00005",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "桑麻沾雨露，燕雀贺生成。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00006",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "好一片烟景也。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00007",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "越大夫在郊外闲来游玩，借观风欲问俗浪迹湖山。行至在山阴道用目观看，遍地里种桑麻岁卜丰年。青是山绿是水花枝灿烂，桃花红柳条绿鸟鹊争喧。一路上观不尽春光无限，但不知苎萝村竟在哪边？",
      "text_length": 88
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00008",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "范蠡下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00009",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "西施上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00010",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "引子",
      "speakers": [
        "西施"
      ],
      "text": "蝶草莺花，惜芳菲，春光无那。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00011",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "西施"
      ],
      "text": "溪水迢迢向若耶，春风处处尽桃花。山深路僻无人问，谁道村西是妾家？",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00012",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "西施"
      ],
      "text": "奴家姓施，名夷光，祖居苎萝村西，因此人都唤做西施。村居荒僻，家道寒微，父母早亡，又无兄弟。貌虽美人莫知，年及笄尚未嫁。赋性坚贞，甘心荆布，年年针线，为他人作嫁衣裳。夜夜辟炉，常向邻家借灯火。看今日天气晴和，不免去到溪边，浣纱便了。",
      "text_length": 115
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00013",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "西施"
      ],
      "text": "自幼儿居住在苎萝村下，生成了美容颜闭月羞花。我爹娘去世早谁怜孤寡，无兄弟少姊妹只剩奴家。插荆钗紧布裾梳妆淡雅，为家贫终日里溪边浣纱。出门来见燕子双飞上下，碧桃花飞片片杨柳交加。",
      "text_length": 88
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00014",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "西施下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00015",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "东施上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00016",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "东施"
      ],
      "text": "人人都说西施俊，我比西施美十分。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00017",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "东施"
      ],
      "text": "奴家东施。为什么叫做东施呢？这倒有个原故。我们这个地方，叫做苎萝村，一村的人，全都姓西。我有一个妹妹，她住在村子西边，她名叫西施；我住在这村子东边，所以就叫东施。只因我妹妹西施，容貌长得也还可以看得，比我的模样，并也不高多少。无奈此地的人，全都恭维她。我未免听见就生气，我说我的容貌，并不含糊，为什么人家都夸她长得好，不夸我呐？我可就留上了神啦。我常常到她家里去，我精心用意地看她，到底是怎么个美法？原来她有个心气疼的病儿，每一犯病，她就两手捧着心口窝，纵着两道眉毛，因此大家就说她是什么眉蹙春山，又是什么捧心西子。我一瞧见，我心里可就明白了。她这么两个把戏，我也不是不会。故此我回到家中，朝夕研究。这几天，我照着镜子学了一学，可就很有点儿像，果然是千姣百媚，真能令人销魂。列位如果不相信，我就学一学，请你们大家看一看，管保叫你们个个动心，回家去一定准害相思病。",
      "text_length": 381
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00018",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "东施捧心做愁，眉一上一下。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00019",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "东施"
      ],
      "text": "就是西施妹妹她看见我这份尊容，她也准得退避三舍。正是：",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00020",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "东施"
      ],
      "text": "若要倾国倾城貌，还须学那多愁多病身。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00021",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "马来！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00022",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "范蠡上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00023",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "一路上观不尽阳春美景，沿溪行水潇潇柳绿垂阴。紧加鞭且把那苎萝村进，又只见柴扉外一树马缨。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00024",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "来此村中，待吾下马，借问一声。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00025",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "范蠡下马，向内。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00026",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "列位请了。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00027",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "请了。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00028",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "借问一声，此处有一东施女子，现在哪里？",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00029",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "马缨花树下，小小门楼便是。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00030",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "有劳了。待我向前问过。吓门上有人么？",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00031",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "东施"
      ],
      "text": "是谁叫门？待奴家去看来。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00032",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "东施开门。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00033",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "东施"
      ],
      "text": "原来是一位客官。您找谁呀？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00034",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "下官范蠡，乃越国大夫。久闻东施大名，特来拜问。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00035",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "东施"
      ],
      "text": "原来是位长官到了，请到里面坐罢。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00036",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "请了。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00037",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "东施"
      ],
      "text": "请坐。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00038",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "有坐。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00039",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "东施"
      ],
      "text": "长官要问那东施，莫非是要与她提亲事吗？",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00040",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "正是。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00041",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "东施"
      ],
      "text": "告便。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00042",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "请便。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00043",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "东施"
      ],
      "text": "可见奴家的芳名，外边都知道了。他既要与我提亲，我倒要高抬声价。",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00044",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "东施转身。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00045",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "东施"
      ],
      "text": "请坐请坐。我说要给东施提亲，倒也容易。但是她长的是沉鱼落雁之容，闭月羞花之貌。要提亲，必须要依她三件大事。",
      "text_length": 53
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00046",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "但不知是哪三件？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00047",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "东施"
      ],
      "text": "第一件必须要王孙公子。非上等社会的人可是不嫁。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00048",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "这第二呢？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00049",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "东施"
      ],
      "text": "第二件要人材出众，相貌出群，总得小白脸才嫁呐。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00050",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "这第三？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00051",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "东施"
      ],
      "text": "第三件要有千金的聘礼。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00052",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "件件依从，必要请来一见。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00053",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "东施"
      ],
      "text": "你要当面相相，使得。你远看——",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00054",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "没有人呐。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00055",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "东施"
      ],
      "text": "你近觑。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00056",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "莫非就是姑娘么？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00057",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "东施"
      ],
      "text": "你看好不好？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00058",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "这个……",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00059",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "东施"
      ],
      "text": "你不用这个那个，你看我身似杨柳，面若芙蓉，眉蹙春山，眼同秋水。",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00060",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "东施做身段。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00061",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "东施"
      ],
      "text": "翩若惊鸿，婉若游龙，国色天姿，世间绝代。看天底下的人，还有再比我长得好的吗？",
      "text_length": 38
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00062",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "好好好，下官要告辞了。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00063",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "东施"
      ],
      "text": "你别走，你倒是提的哪家呀？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00064",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "下官明日再来再讲。少陪了。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00065",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "范蠡转身。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00066",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "好不笑煞我也。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00067",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "范蠡牵马下。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00068",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "东施"
      ],
      "text": "你们看看这个人，慌慌张张，不清不白，他就走啦。我这两样最能够动人的本事，还靡有给他看见呢。他要是看见我这捧心皱眉这两种媚态，只怕他准要酥在这里。他就是想走，也走不动了。看他那样光景，大概一定是看中了，他说明天来，我就等他便了。正是：",
      "text_length": 116
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00069",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "东施"
      ],
      "text": "凭奴百媚千娇态，铁石之人也动心。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00070",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "东施下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00071",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "西施上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00072",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "西施"
      ],
      "text": "蓬门弱女多薄命，溪头浣纱度残生。姻缘未遂苍天定，花枝无主付东风。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00073",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "西施浣纱。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00074",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "马来。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00075",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "范蠡上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00076",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "佳人不遇多扫兴，丑陋女子唬煞人。搅辔停骖忙观定，",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00077",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "呀！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00078",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "溪头坐定一美人。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00079",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "看那溪头有一女子浣纱，待我下马问来。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00080",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "范蠡下马。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00081",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 81,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "吓，娘子请了。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00082",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 82,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "西施"
      ],
      "text": "呀！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00083",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 83,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "西施"
      ],
      "text": "飞花片片随流水，点点清波湿罗裙。溪边转过一人影，停手浣纱把话论。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00084",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 84,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "西施"
      ],
      "text": "吓，客官，敢么是问路的么？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00085",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 85,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "范蠡背供。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00086",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 86,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "这世间果然有此等女子，可算是天姿国色也。吓小娘子，下官得观芳容，莫非采药仙妹，定是避世毛女。但不知娘子家住哪里，姓甚名谁，请道其详。",
      "text_length": 66
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00087",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 87,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "西施"
      ],
      "text": "妾身久住苎萝山下，在若耶溪头。寒家姓施，世居西村，因名西施。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00088",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 88,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "久慕芳名，今幸相遇，不知娘子青春几何？可曾出嫁否？",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00089",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 89,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "西施"
      ],
      "text": "年方二九，尚未适人。请问客官，贵姓高名？",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00090",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 90,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "下官范蠡，官拜越国上大夫之职。久仰芳仪，恨未相见，今日游春到此，竟遇娘子，可谓三生有幸。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00091",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 91,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "西施"
      ],
      "text": "原来是贵人到此，妾有失回避，幸乞恕罪。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00092",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 92,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "岂敢。看娘子丽色美质，真是上界仙人，谪降人世。下官有事相求，未识小娘子可能容纳否？",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00093",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 93,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "西施"
      ],
      "text": "有何金言，当面请讲。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00094",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 94,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "娘子听了！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00095",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 95,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮流水板",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "未曾开言心头恨，尊一声娘子听分明：吴越交兵数年整，一来一往大交兵。吾国懦弱他国胜，因此兵败在会稽城。将吾君臣来囚禁，石室之中受苦情。幸亏文种把贡进，因此才能回朝门。吾国意欲雪仇恨，欲倾吴国进美人。倘若娘子肯应允，万代流芳落美名。",
      "text_length": 114
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00096",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 96,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮流水板",
      "speakers": [
        "西施"
      ],
      "text": "听一言来心自忖，背转身来暗沉吟。只为救国雪耻恨，贱妾怎能惜一身？",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00097",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 97,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "西施"
      ],
      "text": "吴国夫差，性甚残暴，他虽如当年夏桀商纣，妾恐貌丑，难比妹嬉妲己。恐事不成，反留话柄。",
      "text_length": 42
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00098",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 98,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "娘子休得谦辞，待下官明日遣舆，迎接便了。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00099",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 99,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "范蠡"
      ],
      "text": "夫差本是酒色君，国破家亡你要小心。胸中妙计安排定，准备回朝进美人。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00100",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 100,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "范蠡下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00101",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 101,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "西施"
      ],
      "text": "吴王本是残暴君，欺凌越国太无人。夷光若把宫闱进，管叫他锦山河化作灰尘。",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032012_e00102",
      "play_id": "01032012",
      "scene_id": "01032012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 102,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "西施下。",
      "text_length": 4
    }
  ],
  "roles_inferred": true
}